A shriveled corpse wrapped in bandages
This is the body of a tall, musclular man. He is wearing full plate and seems to be quite dead. The fact that the man's head is missing may have something to do with his current condition.
This halfling doesn't seem to have the usual wits of his race.

Value.value: Hullo! You look strong. My... urr... friends had a fellowship of sorts. We be explorin this area and we got ambushed by some big winged fiend. I... I.. too scared to go back! Too dangerous damnit..
Me mates Drerry Rumblebuff, Incanus the Pink, Nalvur Thunderbeard, Maerellion Strongbow, and Roian von Ludersel might still be alive! Look fer me?
Th... This can't be... dis the fiend's sword? My friends? Oh... no... damnit. Here take ye promised goods and leave me be. Yes yes... ye can have some of me soup too.
You done enough thank ye. Be gone and let me suffer in peace.
Anything yet!? Ye found me mates or that nasty fiend?
Be careful of that fiend! If ye happen to slay it ill give you everything me fellowship found recently!

Dogma of Grumbar: The eternal Grumbar is perfect and unchanging. Strive to be more like the eternal one, not to change or allow change to happen. One's given word is the bedrock upon which a stable society is built. To break an oath is to cause a crack in the foundation of civilization. Go forth and spread the word of Grumbar and show through your works the stability and safety he brings.
